{
  "fps": 30,
  "overlap": 14,
  "totalFrames": 4837,
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "dur": 385,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "intro_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Hey — I'm Ruben's AI assistant.",
          "file": "vo/intro_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 69
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Ruben built me — a developer from Germany — and put it all on GitHub.",
          "file": "vo/intro_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 85,
          "dur": 131
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "One day, I'll even make videos like this one myself — that's just not quite live yet.",
          "file": "vo/intro_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 223,
          "dur": 144
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "concept",
      "dur": 771,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "concept_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Personal Jarvis is an AI agent that lives on your computer.",
          "file": "vo/concept_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 112
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "You just talk to it, and it talks back — completely hands-free.",
          "file": "vo/concept_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 128,
          "dur": 106
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "But it's much more than a realtime voice model.",
          "file": "vo/concept_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 241,
          "dur": 75
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_4",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "It's a full agent orchestrator.",
          "file": "vo/concept_4.mp3",
          "localStart": 323,
          "dur": 60
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_5",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "It runs tasks in the background, and actually gets things done for you.",
          "file": "vo/concept_5.mp3",
          "localStart": 390,
          "dur": 116
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_6",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And it runs everywhere — your desktop, a small server, even a browser tab.",
          "file": "vo/concept_6.mp3",
          "localStart": 513,
          "dur": 145
        },
        {
          "id": "concept_7",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Think of it as a home for you, right on your machine.",
          "file": "vo/concept_7.mp3",
          "localStart": 665,
          "dur": 88
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "real_app",
      "dur": 249,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "app_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And this is the actual desktop app.",
          "file": "vo/app_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 64
        },
        {
          "id": "app_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Chat, agents, skills — and an Outputs folder where every result lands.",
          "file": "vo/app_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 80,
          "dur": 151
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "setup_keys",
      "dur": 687,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "keys_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Setting it up takes about a minute, right in the onboarding.",
          "file": "vo/keys_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 93
        },
        {
          "id": "keys_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Jarvis actually uses four kinds of keys.",
          "file": "vo/keys_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 109,
          "dur": 85
        },
        {
          "id": "keys_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "A brain to think, workers for the big jobs, a voice to speak, and ears to listen.",
          "file": "vo/keys_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 201,
          "dur": 162
        },
        {
          "id": "keys_4",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "For each one, you just pick your provider — Claude, OpenAI, Gemini, and more.",
          "file": "vo/keys_4.mp3",
          "localStart": 370,
          "dur": 168
        },
        {
          "id": "keys_5",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "No account to create — you bring your own keys, and you're never locked in.",
          "file": "vo/keys_5.mp3",
          "localStart": 545,
          "dur": 124
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "setup_wake",
      "dur": 285,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "wake_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Next, pick your wake word — the phrase that wakes Jarvis up.",
          "file": "vo/wake_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 108
        },
        {
          "id": "wake_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "I chose Hey Ruben. You can pick anything you like.",
          "file": "vo/wake_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 124,
          "dur": 94
        },
        {
          "id": "wake_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And that's the whole setup.",
          "file": "vo/wake_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 225,
          "dur": 42
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "examples",
      "dur": 386,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "ex_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Once you're set up, you just talk.",
          "file": "vo/ex_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 60
        },
        {
          "id": "ex_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "You can ask it almost anything.",
          "file": "vo/ex_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 76,
          "dur": 48
        },
        {
          "id": "ex_3",
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "What's on my calendar today?",
          "file": "vo/ex_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 131,
          "dur": 70
        },
        {
          "id": "ex_4",
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "Switch the brain to Gemini.",
          "file": "vo/ex_4.mp3",
          "localStart": 208,
          "dur": 76
        },
        {
          "id": "ex_5",
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "Summarise this article for me.",
          "file": "vo/ex_5.mp3",
          "localStart": 291,
          "dur": 77
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "computer_use",
      "dur": 775,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "cu_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Now let me show you two of my favourite features.",
          "file": "vo/cu_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 78
        },
        {
          "id": "cu_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Feature one: Computer Use.",
          "file": "vo/cu_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 94,
          "dur": 60
        },
        {
          "id": "cu_3",
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "Open Chrome and find Elon Musk's latest posts.",
          "file": "vo/cu_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 161,
          "dur": 122
        },
        {
          "id": "cu_4",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Jarvis looks at the screen, reads the interface, moves the mouse, and clicks — exactly like a person would.",
          "file": "vo/cu_4.mp3",
          "localStart": 290,
          "dur": 191
        },
        {
          "id": "cu_5",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "No scripts, no macros. It just uses your computer for you.",
          "file": "vo/cu_5.mp3",
          "localStart": 488,
          "dur": 118
        },
        {
          "id": "cu_6",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And it works across any app on your screen, not just the browser.",
          "file": "vo/cu_6.mp3",
          "localStart": 613,
          "dur": 114
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sub_agents",
      "dur": 722,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "sa_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Feature two: background sub-agents.",
          "file": "vo/sa_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 72
        },
        {
          "id": "sa_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "For the bigger jobs, you just hand off the hard stuff.",
          "file": "vo/sa_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 88,
          "dur": 89
        },
        {
          "id": "sa_3",
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "Write me a deep-dive report on the global EV market.",
          "file": "vo/sa_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 184,
          "dur": 125
        },
        {
          "id": "sa_4",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "It spins up a worker that searches, analyses, and writes the whole thing.",
          "file": "vo/sa_4.mp3",
          "localStart": 316,
          "dur": 129
        },
        {
          "id": "sa_5",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Then it delivers the finished file — while you just keep talking.",
          "file": "vo/sa_5.mp3",
          "localStart": 452,
          "dur": 99
        },
        {
          "id": "sa_6",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And it checks its own work up to three times before you ever see the result.",
          "file": "vo/sa_6.mp3",
          "localStart": 558,
          "dur": 116
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "plugins",
      "dur": 351,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "plug_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "And Jarvis plugs into the tools you already use.",
          "file": "vo/plug_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 85
        },
        {
          "id": "plug_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Gmail, Calendar, Telegram, Discord, Spotify, GitHub — and more.",
          "file": "vo/plug_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 101,
          "dur": 162
        },
        {
          "id": "plug_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "New plugins land all the time.",
          "file": "vo/plug_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 270,
          "dur": 63
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "outro",
      "dur": 352,
      "lines": [
        {
          "id": "outro_1",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "So that's Personal Jarvis — your voice, your computer, your own AI agent.",
          "file": "vo/outro_1.mp3",
          "localStart": 9,
          "dur": 143
        },
        {
          "id": "outro_2",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "It's completely free, and open source.",
          "file": "vo/outro_2.mp3",
          "localStart": 159,
          "dur": 78
        },
        {
          "id": "outro_3",
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "The link is in the description below. Give it a try.",
          "file": "vo/outro_3.mp3",
          "localStart": 244,
          "dur": 90
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
